## Send PW Change SMS Code

> Request

```http
POST <%= config[:version] %>/auth/verification/password/send HTTP/1.1
Host: <%= config[:host] %>
Content-Type: application/json
Content-Length: 32
{
    "phone": "+821093814181"
}
```

```shell
curl --location --request POST '<%= config[:base_url] %>/auth/verification/password/send' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data '{
    "phone": "+821093814181"
}'
```

```javascript
const axios = require('axios');
let data = JSON.stringify({
  "phone": "+821093814181"
});

let config = {
  method: 'post',
  maxBodyLength: Infinity,
  url: '<%= config[:base_url] %>/auth/verification/password/send',
  headers: { 
    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
  },
  data : data
};

axios.request(config)
.then((response) => {
  console.log(JSON.stringify(response.data));
})
.catch((error) => {
  console.log(error);
});
```


사용자의 비밀번호 변경을 위한 SMS 인증 코드를 전송합니다.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config[:version]%>/auth/verification/password/send`

### Scopes

- No permission required

### Response Code

| Code | Description |
| ---- | ----------- |
| 204  | No Content  |

### Error Code

| Code | Message | Description |
| ---- | ------- | ----------- |
| 400 | `INVALID_PHONE_NUMBER` | 유효하지 않은 전화번호 |
| 404 | `NOT_FOUND_USER` | 사용자를 찾을 수 없음 |